webpackJsonp([0xb2e13ad66cdd],{8607:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Carpet Surfing",date:"13 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-13-carpet-surfing/",tags:"Y2009"},html:'<p>At the city festival in Buchholz, the city power utility had a rolling carpet on which one could "surf". Christopher of course had to try it out. He only wiped out twice, but no rug burns. Here are a couple of iPhone snapshots...</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/51035717986@N01/3914904161" title="View \'IMG_0263\' on Flickr.com"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2477/3914904161_074fc057a9.jpg" alt="IMG_0263" border="0" width="375" height="500" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/51035717986@N01/3915682716" title="View \'IMG_0262\' on Flickr.com"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3446/3915682716_e3b50a21f4.jpg" alt="IMG_0262" border="0" width="375" height="500" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/51035717986@N01/3914909707" title="View \'IMG_0264\' on Flickr.com"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3514/3914909707_7fab520f56.jpg" alt="IMG_0264" border="0" width="375" height="500" /></a></p>\n<p>Drinks were being served by the local Junge Union, the youth wing of the CDU party, which I mention only to annoy my German readers (most of whom are not pro-CDU :-).</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Exit Now!",date:"12 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-12-exit-now/"}},previous:{fields:{title:'And the crowd goes "Yeaahh!"',date:"18 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-18-and-the-crowd-goes-yeaahh/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Exit Now!",date:"12 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-12-exit-now/",tags:"Y2009"},html:'<p>It took a bit longer than we hoped, but to make sure you find our restaurant on the Winsener Stra&szlig;e in Hamburg-Harburg we\'ve complemented <a href="http://www.papascott.de/archives/2009/06/27/interesting-drive/">our sign on the A7 southbound</a> before the Fleestedt exit with one for the A7 northbound.</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.papascott.de/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/A-7.jpg" alt="A 7.jpg" border="0" width="450" height="300" /></p>\n<p>It\'s hard to tell from the closeup, but the sign is 12 meters wide and nearly 3 meters high. Here\'s a wider view.</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.papascott.de/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/A-7-1.jpg" alt="A 7-1.jpg" border="0" width="450" height="338" /></p>\n<p>The sign has to be large to make up for a sub-optimal location 1) on the left side of the Autobahn and 2) right before the exit. Like the sign says, you have to exit <em>now</em>!</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Inner Peace",date:"11 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-11-inner-peace/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Carpet Surfing",date:"13 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-13-carpet-surfing/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Inner Peace",date:"11 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-11-inner-peace/",tags:"Y2009"},html:'<p><a href="http://www.papascott.de/archives/2001/09/12/the-day-the-earth-stood-still/">After 8 years</a>, I think I\'ve found peace. Inner peace, anyway. Outer peace is so hard to find these days. Just ask anyone in Afghanistan.</p>\n<p>But what has changed in that time? Not much. The <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamburg_cell#Background">Marienstrasse</a> is still in Hamburg, the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Al-Quds_Mosque">Al-Quds mosque</a> too. We\'ve sent soldiers abroad, more soldiers in Iraq have fallen than those who fell that day into thin air.</p>\n<p>This summer as we were in New York, we took the subway to Ground Zero, to catch a glimpse of hallowed ground. It was a tourist spot, with hawkers and food stands, but inside the fences, even on Saturday, the site was <em>alive</em> with construction work. That comforted me somehow, and we moved on.</p>\n<p>But what has changed? Nothing but the passage of time. Time closes all wounds, but are do the wounds really heal? All wounds leave a scar. I wish I could <a href="http://www.papascott.de/archives/2006/09/10/five-years/">forget that day</a>, but time moves on and the scars remain.</p>\n<p>And so it goes.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"I Gotta Feeling",date:"10 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-10-i-gotta-feeling/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Exit Now!",date:"12 Sep 2009",slug:"/2009-09-12-exit-now/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:51,pageCount:1101}}}});
